Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:27.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\b1}“在陌生人的眼中，街与街之间没有任何区别，我们都知道‘邻里\N情谊’是在哪里画上句号的，在那之后，人们就会…形同陌路。”\N——亚瑟•米勒 著名剧作家 成长于布鲁克林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:56.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rENG}Step on it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:00.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rENG}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\rENG}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不再为我工作了？\N{\rENG}You don't work for me no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:09.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是…难道我没有说我这就去帮他赚钱吗？\N{\rENG}I was just... Didn't I just say I was going to get his money?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,混蛋！我不是为电话公司工作的\N{\rENG}Bitch, I don't work for the phone company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:17.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我大老远跑来不是为了做这种破事儿！你这婊子给我过来！\N{\rENG}I don't do this shit long distance. Bring your ass here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:31.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是我看起来像一堆垃圾，婊子？\N{\rENG}Do I look like I just fell off a turnip truck, bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:37.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你很清楚，鲍勃，近来你的行为有些古怪，你还好吗？\N{\rENG}You know, Bobby, you been acting kind of strange lately. You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是有些小麻烦，可能需要…\N{\rENG}Just had a few personal problems. It's taken care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么麻烦？\N{\rENG}What kind of problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会解决的\N{\rENG}I'll straighten it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:48.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,你确定？\N{\rENG}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然，你不用替我操心\N{\rENG}Absolutely. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,他在干什么？他在打这个女孩\N{\rENG}What's he doing? He's beating this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们那么好运被派到了这里\N{\rENG}We got a 3-million dollar hit about to go down over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不会喜欢的，不要看了\N{\rENG}You don't like it, turn your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这样，吉诺\N{\rENG}Come on, Gino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,伙计们，出动\N{\rENG}Guys, we're coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,吉诺擅自行动了，我们上\N{\rENG}Gino's blowing it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:25.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\rENG}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:29.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怀孕了？！一点小把戏就让你怀孕了？！\N{\rENG}You pregnant?! You let some trick get you pregnant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:31.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,难道你不知道安全套是干什么用的？！\N{\rENG}Ain't you ever heard of a rubber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,这王八蛋打我，我担心我会因此流产\N{\rENG}This motherfucker hit me. I'm scared I'll lose my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这狗娘养的意大利佬！\N{\rENG}You wop motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,你他妈的在干什么？！\N{\rENG}What the fuck you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在和我说话？\N{\rENG}You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你他妈的以为你是谁啊？！\N{\rENG}Who the fuck you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这么喜欢打女人？\N{\rENG}You like to beat up on fucking women?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:06.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来打我啊\N{\rENG}Beat up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,好，很好！\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你住哪，混蛋，我会找到你的老婆和孩子…\N{\rENG}I know where you live, motherfucker. I'll fuck your wife and kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,吉诺，你个婊子养的！\N{\rENG}Gino, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs150}为了正义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有一些没有完成的生意需要去做\N{\rENG}I got some unfinished business to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,今晚都会完成的\N{\rENG}It'll be over by the end of tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟着我干，这些钱就都是你们的\N{\rENG}Stick by me, all that money's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,好多钱啊！\N{\rENG}That's a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们愿意奉陪到底\N{\rENG}We stuck with you through worse for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,但愿今晚能早些结束\N{\rENG}How long could the night be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,妈咪，我能吃个热狗吗？\N{\rENG}Mommy, can I get a hot dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行，宝贝，不要想了，好吗？\N{\rENG}No, honey. Forget about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你现在吃了热狗，那你就吃不下晚饭了\N{\rENG}If you eat a hot dog now, you'll ruin your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:54.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,另外，帮我个忙，今晚你的帆布鞋一定要干净\N{\rENG}Also, do me a favor. IKeep your sneakers clean tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,别弄脏弄湿了，我们今晚要参加聚会的\N{\rENG}No dirt, no puddles. We got a party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,让我们进去买些东西吧，鲍勃，你自己在外面等吧\N{\rENG}Let's go in here to get some stuff. Bobby, I'll take the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,感觉如何，鲍勃？\N{\rENG}How's that feel, Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在你可笑不起来了吧\N{\rENG}You ain't laughing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,还好吗，宝贝？\N{\rENG}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,很好，爸爸，我们能去玩接球游戏吗？\N{\rENG}Good. Dad, can we play catch or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做完功课了吗？\N{\rENG}You finish your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,没做完还想要去玩接球游戏？\N{\rENG}No? And you still want to play catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:22.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧，去拿球吧\N{\rENG}Go get your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,停车，把烟斗给我\N{\rENG}Stop the car. Give me the pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就那样当街杀了个警察\N{\rENG}Doing a cop right in the street like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 把烟斗给我！ - 已经很惹人注意了！\N{\rENG}- Give me the pipe!  - It's already fucking hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还要告诉你们\N{\rENG}I got news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:46.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,今晚结束之前会更惹人注意！\N{\rENG}It'll get a lot hotter before the fucking night's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你那该死的车开走！\N{\rENG}Move the goddamn car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？回车里来！\N{\rENG}What are you doing? Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:56.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你搞什么？\N{\rENG}What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,她死定了\N{\rENG}He'll do her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 王八蛋！ - 王八蛋？\N{\rENG}- Asshole.  - Asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看什么看！\N{\rENG}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,你击球，我来掷球，去拿球棒\N{\rENG}You got the mitt. I got the ball. Get the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,走，我们走\N{\rENG}Let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 吉诺？ - 是我\N{\rENG}- Gino?  - This is me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}出状况了，你能过来吗？\N{\rENG\i1}We got a problem. Can you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和孩子在一起呢，有什么事？\N{\rENG}I'm with the kid, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:50.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在第十八街区，鲍勃·路波被枪杀了，就在他妻子和孩子的面前\N{\rENG\i1}Bobby Lupo was shot on 18th Avenue in front of his wife and kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦，上帝！\N{\rENG}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我会派车去接你的\N{\rENG\i1}I'm sending you a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,维克，我现在得把托尼送你那去\N{\rENG}Vick, I got to send Tony over right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就知道那该死的工作！他为了和你共度周末等了一个月了！\N{\rENG}Damn you and the job! He waits a month for one weekend with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道，可是鲍勃刚才被枪杀了\N{\rENG}I know, but Bobby just got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦，上帝！\N{\rENG}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,当时劳丽和孩子同他在一起\N{\rENG}Laurie and the kids were with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我这就过去，先把托尼送到我父母家吧\N{\rENG}I'll be right over. Send Tony to my parents' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我一会儿过去接他\N{\rENG\i1}I'll pick him up afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,带他们离开这里吧，维克，拜托了\N{\rENG}Get them out of here, Vick, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,你确定你想看看？\N{\rENG}Sure you want to see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,让开一下，让他看看，快点儿\N{\rENG}Give him some room, will you? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,找找还有没有更多的目击证人\N{\rENG}See if there are any more witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前只有个卖水果的家伙看到了一切\N{\rENG}All I got is this fruit and vegetable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,真的很难过，吉诺，是理查·马德诺干的\N{\rENG}I'm real sorry, Gino. It was Richie Madano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,劳丽说，理查下了车就径直走了过去，然后“砰”就开枪了\N{\rENG}Laurie said Richie got out of the car and just stepped up. Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:36.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,卖水果的说理查扔下了什么东西，可是我们什么也没发现\N{\rENG}The grocer said Richie tossed something. We didn't find nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:41.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们都知道该怎么惩治罪犯\N{\rENG}We know every mob operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们会揪出他们，迫使他们投降\N{\rENG}We'll squeeze them to give him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:48.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,尽管去做吧，但找到这帮混蛋的会是我，你很清楚的\N{\rENG}Do that. But it's me who'll find this fucking guy. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和维克…\N{\rENG}You and Vicky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:53.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个月我们就要离婚了\N{\rENG}Divorce goes through this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,是怎么一回事？\N{\rENG}How'd it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:59.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,是理查·马德诺，某个自作聪明的混蛋\N{\rENG}Some wannabe wiseguy asshole, Richie Madano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,毒贩子，他自己也吸毒\N{\rENG}Dope dealer, dope user...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是和吉诺、鲍勃一起长大的\N{\rENG}He was a guy Bobby and Gino grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不清楚他为什么要杀鲍勃\N{\rENG}We don't know why he'd kill Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rENG}sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我一会儿\N{\rENG}Wait for me for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:19.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗？ - 不，很不好！他是我最好的朋友！\N{\rENG}- Are you all right?  - No, I'm not! He was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,他刚才把一个女人从车里拉出来…\N{\rENG}He just pulled a woman out of a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,射穿了她的脑袋，这似乎很不合常理\N{\rENG}...and blew her brains out. It looks random.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:31.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,他身边还有三个小弟，其中一个在脖子上有纹身\N{\rENG}Three of his crew were with him. One has a tattoo on his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道他是谁，波奇\N{\rENG}I know him. Bochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,他就是堆狗屎，他的犯罪记录和我的胳膊一样长\N{\rENG}He's a piece of shit. Got a sheet as long as my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:39.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们要搜索整个城市，每名警员都出动了\N{\rENG}We got a city-wide out, every officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,在机场、火车站、公共汽车站都有我们的人\N{\rENG}We got A.L.'s at the airports, trains, buses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,这混蛋不会逃跑的\N{\rENG}This guy won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,他会躲起来，但决不会离开布鲁克林\N{\rENG}He'll sneak and hide, but he won't leave Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:52.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你他的每个毒窝在哪，但你得让我用我的方式来解决这件事\N{\rENG}I'll feed you every dope dive he's got, but let me do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,给我一辆没记号的车和一把散弹枪\N{\rENG}Just give me an unmarked and a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这样，你太过深入了，让其他警察去处理吧\N{\rENG}Don't. You're too close. Let other cops do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我比这的任何人都更了解那个混蛋\N{\rENG}I know this guy better than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:13.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我比其他任何人都更知道这儿的邻里关系\N{\rENG}I know the neighborhood better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 那小心点，好吗？ - 你了解我的\N{\rENG}- Be careful, will you?  - You know me.
