Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.83,0:34:25.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,这儿有很多拳击的大事记嘛\N{\rENG}I've noticed a lot of boxing memorabilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.30,0:34:29.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,到处都是手套\N{\rENG}We got some gloves over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.44,0:34:32.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,到处都是照片，那个拳击手是谁？\N{\rENG}Pictures everywhere. Who's the boxer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:34.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,你？你就是那个硬汉？\N{\rENG}You're the boxer? You a tough guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.34,0:34:38.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 真屌啊  - 是吗？你会点什么？\N{\rENG}- Tough enough.  - Really? What could you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.61,0:34:39.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,就你？\N{\rENG}To you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.29,0:34:49.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,我心情开始变差了\N{\rENG}I'm starting to get in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.46,0:34:53.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许就只一种心情的波动，荷尔蒙，或者是一种压抑已久的欲望\N{\rENG}Maybe it's a mood swing, my hormones, or a need to impose my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.20,0:34:57.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我要你告诉他们叫他们到桌子上去\N{\rENG\i1}I want you tell these finocchis to get on the fucking table.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.63,0:35:02.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,叫他们到桌子上去\N{\rENG}Tell them to get up on the fucking table.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.30,0:35:07.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？你会杀了楼上的人！\N{\rENG}Are you totally nuts?! You could've killed somebody upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.41,0:35:09.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 但是楼上可没人  - 你又怎么知道的？\N{\rENG}- But there's nobody upstairs!  - How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.30,0:35:11.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,你搜索过这个酒吧吗？\N{\rENG}Did you bust in the joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.02,0:35:15.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,不记得了\N{\rENG}I don't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.37,0:35:18.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,能让他那么有种的也就是那警徽和枪\N{\rENG}The only balls he has is that badge and gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.78,0:35:28.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是我的枪！\N{\rENG}Here's my gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.65,0:35:32.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,游戏公平了，这是我的警徽\N{\rENG}Fair game now, okay? And here's my badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:35.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是你们的奖杯，这是你们的奖杯，好了吧？\N{\rENG}This is your trophy. This is your trophy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.79,0:35:37.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来拿啊\N{\rENG}Come and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.20,0:35:40.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}叫那些人来拿呀\N{\rENG\i1}Tell one of your citriolis to come and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.53,0:35:43.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,拿到警徽者重奖5000美元\N{\rENG}I offer 5000 for that badge, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.00,0:35:48.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,有人看见理查了吗？\N{\rENG}Anybody see Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.41,0:35:52.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有人知道为什么理查要杀鲍勃？\N{\rENG}Anybody know why Richie did Bobby Lupo?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.01,0:35:56.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,小子，你想过我这关？\N{\rENG}Fuckface, you want to get by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.51,0:36:00.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,只有两件事能阻止你：恐惧和常识\N{\rENG}There's only two things stopping you: Fear and common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.82,0:36:02.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我现在要把你的头砍下来！\N{\rENG}And I'll cut your fucking head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.90,0:36:15.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这个操蛋，你把我的牙打掉了！\N{\rENG}You motherfucker! You knocked my teeth out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.50,0:36:19.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿，拿球杆的，给我上！\N{\rENG}Hey, Sticks, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.47,0:36:59.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,妈的！\N{\rENG}Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.65,0:37:14.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是维托理奥的人\N{\rENG}I'm with Vittorio.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.18,0:37:17.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,也就意味着你不能碰我\N{\rENG}So that means you can't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.92,0:37:21.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错，我忘了\N{\rENG}That's right. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.86,0:37:30.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好吗，伙计？\N{\rENG}How you doing, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.83,0:37:34.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我想和你兄弟谈谈  - 他会找你谈谈的，你这只猪！\N{\rENG}- I want to talk to your brother.  - He'll want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.17,0:37:38.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？你不能这样做\N{\rENG}What are you doing? You don't want to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.21,0:37:43.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,你去告诉你兄弟我会把他的头砍下来往他喉咙里小便\N{\rENG}Tell him I'll cut off his head and piss down his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.43,0:37:44.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,去你的！\N{\rENG}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.32,0:38:00.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,有人看到过理查吗？\N{\rENG}Anybody seen Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.52,0:38:06.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会经常光临，直到有人记得看到过理查！\N{\rENG}I'm going to keep coming back until somebody remembers seeing Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.16,0:40:39.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,有什么消息？\N{\rENG}So what's the latest?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.66,0:40:42.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,消息是：满城都是警察在我们的店里守侯伏击\N{\rENG}The cops are all over town, hitting every business we own.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.13,0:40:45.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我派出所有的手下上街去找那个杂种\N{\rENG}All my guys are looking for this bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.83,0:40:48.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,维托理奥，他正在无法无天地杀人！\N{\rENG}Vittorio, he's killing people like it was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.07,0:40:51.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我游好了我要去科诺吃饭\N{\rENG}When I'm through, I'm going to Cono's for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.67,0:40:53.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你务必找到吉诺\N{\rENG}You find Gino.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.34,0:40:56.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,叫他…就叫他去那里见我\N{\rENG}Tell him to... Ask him to meet me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.64,0:40:58.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,你去找到理查，不管用什么方法\N{\rENG}And you find Richie. I don't care how.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.68,0:41:00.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是要找到他\N{\rENG}You just find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.41,0:41:02.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rENG}I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.72,0:41:11.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 告诉乔伊老鼠的事  - 什么老鼠？\N{\rENG}- Tell Joey about the mouse.  - What mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.72,0:41:15.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 他现在不是个灭鼠专家吗？ - 那老鼠是怎么回事？\N{\rENG}- Why, is Joey an exterminator now?  - What about the mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.39,0:41:19.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我家里有一只老鼠，我花了八百美元去抓它\N{\rENG}I got a mouse in my house. I pay $800 so I can chase a mouse around.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.73,0:41:20.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,就为了杀了那杂种耗子\N{\rENG}Shoot this rat bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.23,0:41:24.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,那老鼠只有这么点，你叫我用枪去打？\N{\rENG}The mouse is about this fucking big. I'm going to shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.90,0:41:26.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,朝地上开一枪，有可能杀掉楼下邻居\N{\rENG}Shoot him through the floor, you kill a neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.74,0:41:29.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们去买捕鼠器吧\N{\rENG}Let's go by Chas the Chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.26,0:41:32.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想那老鼠要比你聪明吧\N{\rENG}I think the mouse is smarter than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.74,0:41:35.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 就用枪打吧  - 不准再说耗子的事！\N{\rENG}- Shoot this rat.  - Shut up about the fucking mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.75,0:41:46.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你赶来\N{\rENG}Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.75,0:41:49.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 请坐  - 坐在我看得见你的地方\N{\rENG}- Pull up a chair.  - Sit where I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.42,0:41:58.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们警察为什么要满城地搜我的地方？\N{\rENG}What are your guys...? Busting my balls all over town?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.33,0:42:01.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,坏了我的生意，这样不对，吉诺\N{\rENG}Hurting my business. That ain't right, Gino.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.33,0:42:06.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯，你是知道的，维托理奥，我是想告诉你…\N{\rENG}Well, you know, Vittorio, I was meaning to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.00,0:42:08.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不是很喜欢你\N{\rENG}...I really don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.10,0:42:11.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,并且我从来都没喜欢过你\N{\rENG}And I never really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.94,0:42:16.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你跌落悬崖或者被捕了，终日铁窗生涯\N{\rENG}If you fall off a cliff or get arrested, rot in jail for life...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.34,0:42:18.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一点都不在乎，好吗？\N{\rENG}...I really don't care, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.68,0:42:26.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,对于鲍勃的事我深感抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm sorry about what happened to Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.75,0:42:27.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你很爱他\N{\rENG}I know how you loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.36,0:42:31.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我知道你刚才的一句话是言不由衷的\N{\rENG}But I know you don't mean one word you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.69,0:42:34.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是我们的一分子\N{\rENG}You're one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.33,0:42:35.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,家人\N{\rENG}Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.63,0:42:39.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你\N{\rENG}Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.53,0:42:42.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是你们的一分子，我也不是你们的人\N{\rENG}I'm not one of you, and I'm not with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.04,0:42:55.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,吉诺，等等\N{\rENG}Gino, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.14,0:43:00.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么可以那样和一个老人说话？\N{\rENG}Why you talking to the old man like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.21,0:43:04.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为他是你的头儿，不是我的，懂我的意思吗？\N{\rENG}Because he's your boss, not mine. You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.85,0:43:06.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要告诉你一件事\N{\rENG}I want to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.05,0:43:08.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还记得皮诺叔叔，对吧？\N{\rENG}You remember Uncle Pino, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.39,0:43:10.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊，那个高个儿\N{\rENG}Yeah. The big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.32,0:43:12.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,有一次…\N{\rENG}One time...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.22,0:43:17.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,当我还小的时候，皮诺叔叔打算带我去看电影\N{\rENG}...when I was a kid, Pino was going to take me to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.00,0:43:20.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们先去了糖果店，叫麦提阿莫的一家店，还记得吗？\N{\rENG}First, we go to the candy store. Mettiamo's, remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.23,0:43:22.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁会忘记呢？\N{\rENG}Who the hell could forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.73,0:43:25.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们看见有个人抢劫那家店，大把大把地往口袋里塞钱\N{\rENG}We see this guy filling up his pockets with this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.07,0:43:27.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,皮诺叔叔抓住他的喉咙\N{\rENG}Pino grabs him by the throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.74,0:43:30.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,把他拖到外面，狠狠地给了他一顿拳脚\N{\rENG}...drags him outside, throws him a beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.11,0:43:35.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后把他扔到后备箱里，开车去电影院了\N{\rENG}Puts him in the trunk of the car, drives to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.18,0:43:37.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,他还去看电影？\N{\rENG}He went to the movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:42.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,在影院里，我没有在看电影，我一直在想…\N{\rENG}In the movies, I'm not watching. I'm thinking to myself:
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.09,0:43:45.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,“后备箱里的那个人会怎么样呢？”\N{\rENG}"What about this guy in the trunk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.03,0:43:51.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想：叔叔杀了他，他已经死了\N{\rENG}I think to myself, "He killed him. He's dead. "
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.26,0:43:54.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我跑向皮诺叔叔，说：“你把那个人杀了”\N{\rENG}I run to Pino, I says, "You killed the guy. "
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.93,0:43:58.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,皮诺叔叔烦了，就把我带到车前，给了我钥匙，然后说：\N{\rENG}Pino's bored, brings me around the front, gives me the keys, he says:
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.94,0:44:00.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,“做你该做的事”\N{\rENG}"Do what you got to do. "
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.93,0:44:03.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我说：“我？我能做什么？我才九岁”\N{\rENG}I says, "Me? What am I going to do? I'm nine years old. "
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.36,0:44:07.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,他给我钥匙，我打开了后备箱\N{\rENG}He gives me the keys. I open the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.40,0:44:09.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我看见一个人盯着我看  - 你一定被吓到了\N{\rENG}- I see a man staring at me.  - You must've been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.27,0:44:12.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,皮诺叔叔就在旁边，有什么好怕的？\N{\rENG}I've got Pino over here. What am I scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.87,0:44:16.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我对那个人说：“嘿，你，给我滚出来！”\N{\rENG}I says to the guy, "Hey you, get the fuck out of here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.78,0:44:20.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,眨眼之间他就不见了\N{\rENG}I blink. He's in Hoboken.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.51,0:44:21.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像离弦之箭？\N{\rENG}He took off like a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.72,0:44:23.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,简直像只鸟\N{\rENG}Like a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.28,0:44:24.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一定把他吓得屁滚尿流\N{\rENG}You scared the shit out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.72,0:44:27.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个狗娘养的\N{\rENG}The son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.29,0:44:32.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,九岁啊，我看着皮诺叔叔，心里想：\N{\rENG}Nine years old, I'm looking at Pino, I'm thinking to myself:
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.23,0:44:35.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,“天啊！叔叔真是个伟大的人”\N{\rENG}"My God, what a great guy. "
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.73,0:44:38.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一直想做个聪明人\N{\rENG}I always wanted to be a wiseguy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.13,0:44:41.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看我们，在神之下\N{\rENG}Look at us now, under God.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.64,0:44:44.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁会想到我会成为一名警察？\N{\rENG}Who'd have thought that I would've become a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.24,0:44:46.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿，幸运儿，你要知道…\N{\rENG}Hey, Lucky, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.14,0:44:50.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,对我来说，神只是个操纵者\N{\rENG}...to me God's a puppeteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.31,0:44:53.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们只不过在任他操纵而已\N{\rENG}We're on the end of the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.81,0:44:56.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是神有一种独特的幽默感，这你得承认\N{\rENG}But God has a strange sense of humor, you got to admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.32,0:44:59.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许你是对的\N{\rENG}Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.27,0:45:23.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,理查，从你突然变成名人来判断…\N{\rENG}Richie, judging by your sudden rise to stardom...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.83,0:45:26.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,…我打赌这上面应该有个牌子了\N{\rENG}...I'll lay odds this one's got a make on it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.17,0:45:29.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,理查，别！别这样，你在干什么？\N{\rENG}Richie, don't! Don't! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.18,0:45:32.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是一夜成名啊，宝贝儿\N{\rENG}I'm an overnight success, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.94,0:45:36.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要在这儿玩一会儿，有意见吗？\N{\rENG}I'm going to crib here for a couple hours. Any problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.15,0:46:14.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,要我怎么相信那是真的？\N{\rENG}How do I know that thing's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.05,0:46:18.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看上去不像是个正直的人吗？你能把我想得多坏呢？\N{\rENG}Don't I look like an honest guy? How bad do you want to find out?
