Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.70,0:55:34.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，那是抢劫，不是贩毒\N{\rENG}Jerry, that's robbery, not narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.93,0:55:38.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,找丹齐格谈谈然后再来找我\N{\rENG}Talk to Donziger and get back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.54,0:55:40.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要和你谈谈\N{\rENG}I'll talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.19,0:55:59.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,这看上去熟悉吗？\N{\rENG}Does this look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.70,0:56:10.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行，我要是帮你了，他会杀了我的\N{\rENG}I can't. I help you any way, he'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.07,0:56:12.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜托，他是你的亲兄弟啊\N{\rENG}Come on. He's your own brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.97,0:56:16.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,他简直就像个吸尘器，他一次能吸三到四克毒品\N{\rENG}He's a vacuum. He sucks up 3 to 4 grams a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.44,0:56:18.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,那么大的量对理性思维可没什么帮助\N{\rENG}That much crack doesn't promote rational thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.91,0:56:22.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样情况会越来越糟糕的\N{\rENG}It'll get worse than I been telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.35,0:56:24.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也逮捕了你的父亲\N{\rENG}I got your father under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.48,0:56:26.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,没用的，吉诺！\N{\rENG}It won't work, Gino!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.48,0:56:28.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊，你怎么就不懂呢？\N{\rENG}God! Why don't you understand this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.15,0:56:31.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们没法帮你\N{\rENG}We can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.89,0:56:34.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,他要知道我们帮了你，他会连爸爸一起杀掉！\N{\rENG}If he even thinks we did, he'll kill Pop too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.32,0:56:35.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,他有那么离谱了？\N{\rENG}He's that far gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.53,0:56:37.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还是相信吧，吉诺\N{\rENG}Believe it, Gino.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.98,0:56:39.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,任何人\N{\rENG}Anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.80,0:56:42.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样的话，今晚我要把你留在这里好让你保命\N{\rENG}Then I'm going to keep you here tonight and keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.22,0:56:44.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,明天再恨我吧\N{\rENG}Hate me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.33,0:56:53.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在八〇区\N{\rENG\i1}In the 8-0 precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.10,0:56:58.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}信号一〇一三，警员遭袭，安博伊大街，六八三五号\N{\rENG\i1}Signal 1013. Police officer shot. 6835 Amboy Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.34,0:57:03.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,今晚将是这个城市难以忘怀的一个晚上\N{\rENG}This is one night this town ain't never going to forget about.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.68,0:57:06.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,问问我，我想你已经万事具备了\N{\rENG}Ask me, I think you already made sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.51,0:57:10.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你的妻子打来几次电话，她和托尼一起在你的公寓里\N{\rENG\i1}Your wife's called couple times. She's at your apartment with Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.72,0:57:13.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}能不能抽空过来一下呢？\N{\rENG\i1}Any chance you can swing over there for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.89,0:57:17.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行，我正在巡逻\N{\rENG}I could do that. I'm right in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.96,0:57:22.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,来，过来\N{\rENG}Come over here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.37,0:57:29.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我都差点忘了你了\N{\rENG}I almost forgot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.37,0:57:33.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我得给你洗个热水澡，再弄点食物\N{\rENG}I got to get you a nice hot bath, some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.37,0:57:36.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许再给你弄个女朋友吧\N{\rENG}Maybe a girlfriend or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.73,0:58:01.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,托尼好吗？\N{\rENG}How's Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.93,0:58:02.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,他很好\N{\rENG}He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.66,0:58:06.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,你吃饭了吗？\N{\rENG}Did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.23,0:58:09.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,吃了几块狗饼干\N{\rENG}A couple of dog biscuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.63,0:58:11.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 这是新来的狗  - 看看啊\N{\rENG}- This is my new dog.  - Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.07,0:58:15.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是警犬？ - 它叫寇利吉奥\N{\rENG}- A police dog?  - This is Corragio.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.67,0:58:17.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要收留它吗？\N{\rENG}Are you keeping him?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.91,0:58:19.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是这么想的\N{\rENG}I'm thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.68,0:58:23.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许吧，着取决于它有多勇敢\N{\rENG}Maybe. It depends on how brave he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.02,0:58:27.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我最好去回去看看托尼\N{\rENG}I'd better go and see Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.42,0:58:34.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,想上来吃点东西吗？\N{\rENG}You want to come up for an espresso?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.86,0:58:36.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,好啊，为什么不呢？\N{\rENG}Yeah. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.03,0:58:40.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,好好呆在那儿，乖孩子\N{\rENG}You stay there and be a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.87,0:58:47.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 要把狗给托尼看看吗？ - 那他就睡不着觉了\N{\rENG}- Should we show the dog to Tony?  - He'll never go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.40,0:58:50.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,你小时候养过狗吗？\N{\rENG}Did you ever have a dog when you were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.37,0:58:54.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,开玩笑，我们连自己都没办法吃饱\N{\rENG}We didn't have enough money to feed ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.81,0:58:58.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还小的时候，这个居民区里来了一个老人\N{\rENG}There was this old man who came to the neighborhood when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.22,0:59:02.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是从偏远的乡下来的\N{\rENG}He was from the old country.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.72,0:59:04.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,他带着一个古老的铃铛\N{\rENG}He carried an old school bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.22,0:59:09.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,他有一个脚踏的磨刀器\N{\rENG}He pulled along a sharpening machine operated by a foot peddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.40,0:59:16.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,邻居们就叫他把自家的刀和剪刀磨锋利\N{\rENG}The neighbors used to get their knives and scissors sharpened.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.46,0:59:18.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,一角钱或者两角钱\N{\rENG}A dime here, a quarter there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.06,0:59:20.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这是种诚实的谋生方式\N{\rENG}But it was an honest living.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.39,0:59:22.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,日子一天天地过去…\N{\rENG}Time goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.13,0:59:24.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,…人们逐渐开始买…\N{\rENG}...people start buying...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.06,0:59:27.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,多功能的刀和剪刀了\N{\rENG}...disposable scissors and knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.47,0:59:30.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,越来越少的人找他磨刀\N{\rENG}Fewer and fewer people come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.14,0:59:32.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我总是在想…\N{\rENG}I always used to think to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.41,0:59:35.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,…他这样地…\N{\rENG}...how it would feel to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.64,0:59:37.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,…早出晚归…\N{\rENG}...before light...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.91,0:59:39.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,…又没什么收获给家人看…\N{\rENG}...and come back after dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.91,0:59:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,…是一种什么感觉呢…\N{\rENG}...with nothing to show your wife and family for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.09,0:59:50.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,那铃声是我听到过的最孤独的声音\N{\rENG}That bell was the loneliest sound I ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.89,0:59:54.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个老人就是你父亲吧？\N{\rENG}He was your father, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.43,1:00:01.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,我记得我一度跟了他一个夏天…\N{\rENG}I remember one time I followed the old man for a whole summer...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.40,1:00:02.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,…每天…\N{\rENG}...every day...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.90,1:00:04.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,…从日出到日落\N{\rENG}...day in, day out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.77,1:00:10.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,过了一段时间，这开始令他倍受煎熬\N{\rENG}And after a while, it started to grind him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.11,1:00:14.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,没人，没人再需要他了，你知道吗？\N{\rENG}Nobody, nobody needs him, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.78,1:00:17.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得没人再需要你了…\N{\rENG}If you feel like nobody needs you...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.12,1:00:20.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,…如果你觉得自己毫无用处了…\N{\rENG}...and you feel useless...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.39,1:00:26.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,…你的心就死了\N{\rENG}...you die inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.62,1:00:32.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就没了生存的欲望\N{\rENG}You let yourself go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.89,1:00:37.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们总是告诉别人：“爸爸死于癌症”\N{\rENG}We always used to tell everybody, "Pop died from cancer. "
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.19,1:00:40.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,可是我相信，他死于一颗破碎的心\N{\rENG}I believe he died of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.73,1:00:43.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸爸死后…\N{\rENG}After Pop died...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.83,1:00:48.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,附近的孩子想要去科尼岛玩…\N{\rENG}...and the neighborhood kids wanted to go to Coney Island to play...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.97,1:00:52.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,…有那么一个父亲，马德诺先生…\N{\rENG}...one of the other fathers, Mr. Madano...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.91,1:00:56.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,…会偷偷给我一点钱，让我可以和别的孩子一起玩\N{\rENG}...used to slip me a little money so I could go play with the kids too.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.35,1:01:06.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道我是怎么报答马德诺先生的吗？\N{\rENG}You know how I repay Mr. Madano?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.49,1:01:08.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想知道今晚我是如何感激他的吗？\N{\rENG}You want to know how I thanked him tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.93,1:01:11.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,我逮捕了他\N{\rENG}I arrested him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.00,1:01:13.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样我才能找到理查\N{\rENG}Just so I could get to Richie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.77,1:01:17.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就是那么个疯子\N{\rENG}That's how crazy I get.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.17,1:01:23.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,吉诺，这里是你的管辖区域…\N{\rENG}Gino, these may be your streets and your neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.54,1:01:26.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,…但是还有别的警察啊\N{\rENG}...but there are other police officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.18,1:01:29.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我为你的所做而感到自豪\N{\rENG}I'm really proud of what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.68,1:01:34.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道每个人都很爱你\N{\rENG}And I know how everybody loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.95,1:01:37.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但托尼需要一个父亲…\N{\rENG}But Tony needs a father...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.86,1:01:40.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,…我也需要一个丈夫\N{\rENG}...and I need a husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.36,1:01:46.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿干什么？重叙旧好？\N{\rENG}What are we talking, reconciliation over here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.96,1:01:49.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,不，我们在谈人生\N{\rENG}No, we're talking a lifetime deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.12,1:01:52.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,不论拥有一切抑或一无所有\N{\rENG}All or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.46,1:01:55.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能做到\N{\rENG}I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.46,1:01:57.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以做到\N{\rENG}That I could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.21,1:02:12.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rENG}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.83,1:02:36.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 托尼！托尼在哪儿？ - 躲到浴缸里\N{\rENG}- Tony! We need Tony!  - Get down in the bathtub!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.74,1:02:37.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的，浴缸里\N{\rENG}In the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.60,1:03:18.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你死定了\N{\rENG}You're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.88,1:03:29.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,来啊，你这个叛徒！\N{\rENG}Come on, you rat bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.52,1:03:36.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,扔了它\N{\rENG}Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.22,1:03:40.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想对一个手无寸铁的人开枪？\N{\rENG}You going to shoot an unarmed man?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.22,1:03:43.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然不会，你知道我要做什么？\N{\rENG}I wouldn't. You know what I'm going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.43,1:03:45.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这个王八蛋！\N{\rENG}You motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.91,1:04:00.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,安琪儿，派几个人到我家来\N{\rENG}Angie, send me units over to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.91,1:04:04.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我这里发生了枪击案\N{\rENG\i1}There's been a shooting over at my place.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.41,1:04:07.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是一群理查的手下，他们已经被我打死了\N{\rENG\i1}It's a bunch of Richie Madano's crew. They're all deceased.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.02,1:04:18.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要送你和你妈妈去宾馆\N{\rENG}Going to take you to a hotel with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.85,1:04:26.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道这件事不好解决，你也很害怕\N{\rENG}I know that this is not an easy thing and I know you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.36,1:04:28.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会把它解决的\N{\rENG}I'll take care of it right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.93,1:04:34.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦，妈的！\N{\rENG}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.44,1:04:38.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,伙计…\N{\rENG}Fellas...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.11,1:04:40.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,…来杯饮料吧\N{\rENG}...have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.37,1:04:41.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,不必了\N{\rENG}Never mind that bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.77,1:04:42.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,你给我坐下\N{\rENG}Sit down, dickhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.01,1:04:46.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在找你的兄弟，他在哪儿？\N{\rENG}We're looking for your brother. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.51,1:04:49.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,他没来过，我没见过他\N{\rENG}He ain't been around. I ain't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.58,1:04:51.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你听得懂英语吗？\N{\rENG}You understand English?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.38,1:04:52.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,教他点英文吧\N{\rENG}Teach this guy some English.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.29,1:04:56.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,你这个小杂碎，快说！\N{\rENG}You fucking bum. You want to give me the right answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.39,1:04:58.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,你兄弟在哪儿？\N{\rENG}Where's your fucking brother? You cocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.96,1:05:00.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,不然我打烂你的头！\N{\rENG}I'll break your fucking head!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.23,1:05:05.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们两个都死定了！你们两个！告诉他\N{\rENG}You're both dead, you fucking bums! The two of you! Tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.63,1:05:09.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,就说拉斯特说你们死定了，你们两个人！\N{\rENG}Say Rusty told you you're dead! The two of yous!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.07,1:05:15.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,王八蛋！\N{\rENG}You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.58,1:05:25.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们都滚出去！\N{\rENG}Get the fuck out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.24,1:05:29.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,快从这里滚出去！\N{\rENG}Get the fuck out of here, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.49,1:05:34.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我打赌你在你那片很出名了\N{\rENG\i1}I bet you're real popular in your neighborhood now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.43,1:05:37.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,安琪儿，我一向不怎么受欢迎\N{\rENG}Angie, I was never too popular with my neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.92,1:05:39.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要去拉莫尔了\N{\rENG}I'm heading to Lamore's now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.84,1:05:59.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,派蒂回来了吗？\N{\rENG}Patti back yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.78,1:06:02.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以和你私下里谈谈吗？\N{\rENG}Can I talk to you in private for a minute, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.78,1:06:08.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\rENG}Sit over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.52,1:06:15.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个人是你？\N{\rENG}Is this you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.53,1:06:17.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我叫泰利·马隆\N{\rENG}My name's Terry Malloy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.29,1:06:19.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,那洛葛仙妮是谁？\N{\rENG}So who's Roxanne?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.96,1:06:22.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,理查的女朋友，我以为你们都在找她\N{\rENG}Richie's girlfriend. I thought that's who you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.80,1:06:25.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,的确，你知道我在哪儿能找到她吗？\N{\rENG}It is. Do you know where I can find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.97,1:06:29.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只知道她住在布鲁克林，但不知道哪里\N{\rENG}I think she lives here in Brooklyn, but I don't know where.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.37,1:06:32.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道哪里，你是什么？一个关心大事的公民了？\N{\rENG}You don't know where. What are you, a concerned citizen now?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.31,1:06:34.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,为什么不？\N{\rENG}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.44,1:06:35.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,理查和你什么关系？\N{\rENG}Who is Richie to you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.38,1:06:37.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是一坨屎\N{\rENG}A piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.08,1:06:40.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么看上去像是刚哭过？\N{\rENG}How come you look like you been crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.64,1:06:44.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有偏头痛\N{\rENG}I got a fucking migraine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.06,1:06:49.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,听着，我要问你点事\N{\rENG}Listen, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.16,1:06:51.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你认识这个女孩吗？\N{\rENG}Do you know this girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.99,1:06:59.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你先给我坐在这里\N{\rENG}Maybe you could sit over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.39,1:07:01.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\rENG}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.76,1:07:04.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜托，泰利\N{\rENG}Come on, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.23,1:07:08.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你得告诉我\N{\rENG}You have to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.41,1:07:13.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,她到底是谁？\N{\rENG}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.01,1:07:15.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,她是洛葛仙妮\N{\rENG}It's Roxanne.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.74,1:07:19.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你跟鲍勃同时都和她上床？\N{\rENG}And you were fucking Bobby at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.18,1:07:23.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这样，来，稳定一下情绪\N{\rENG}Don't be that way. Come on. Settle down.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.49,1:07:29.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,你姓什么？\N{\rENG}She got a last name?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.19,1:07:31.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,福特，我叫洛葛仙妮·福特\N{\rENG}Ford. Roxanne Ford.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.62,1:08:13.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好吗，沃米尔？\N{\rENG}How you doing, Vermeer?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.29,1:08:18.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是怎么来的？天啊！\N{\rENG}How the hell did you get up here, man? Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.23,1:08:22.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,他和这件事无关\N{\rENG}He didn't have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.91,1:08:39.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了？我们在这里等了你一个晚上\N{\rENG}Where you been? We been waiting around here all night for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.65,1:08:46.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在等什么呢？\N{\rENG}What you been waiting on?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.32,1:08:49.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在等什么？\N{\rENG}What you been waiting on?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.93,1:08:51.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看你是否需要我们，想喝点什么？\N{\rENG}Waiting on if you need us. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.99,1:08:53.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的鼻子怎么了？\N{\rENG}What happened to your nose?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.00,1:08:59.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,吉诺仗着警察的身份，把场子砸了\N{\rENG}Gino came around, playing the role. Busting up the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.67,1:09:01.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么？你们没有武器？\N{\rENG}What, you ain't got a piece?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.01,1:09:05.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,吧台后面不是有枪吗？\N{\rENG}You got a piece behind the bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.28,1:09:09.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就让他打了你的脸？你怎么不扁他？\N{\rENG}You let him do that to your face? Why didn't you whack him?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.55,1:09:12.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只知道你杀了鲍勃，你叫我攻击一个警察？\N{\rENG}All I heard was you clipped Bobby. You want me to whack a cop too?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.11,1:09:17.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,没人担心你被人打对吧？\N{\rENG}Nobody has to worry about you stepping on your dick.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.29,1:09:24.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道他有多厉害，而且你又把鲍勃杀了！\N{\rENG}You know how wacko he gets! And with you doing Bobby like that!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.18,1:09:28.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们把我和一个小杂碎搞反了\N{\rENG}You're mistaking me for someone who gives a shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.02,1:09:31.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果吉诺跟我对着干…\N{\rENG}If Gino and me bang heads...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.86,1:09:33.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,…我就让他进棺材\N{\rENG}...he'll be racked in a closed casket.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.13,1:09:37.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不会让他抓到你？\N{\rENG}You won't let him take you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.53,1:09:40.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是什么？小丑吗？\N{\rENG}What are you, a clown?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.87,1:09:45.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,抓到我？把我抓去哪儿？\N{\rENG}Take me? Take me where?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.88,1:09:55.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们叫一个混蛋弄成这样！\N{\rENG}You let one motherfucker take you!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.48,1:10:00.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,不单单只有吉诺！还有别人满街地砸我们的门\N{\rENG}It ain't just Gino! Bulls are banging down doors all over the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.52,1:10:03.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,是弗兰齐他们，他们回来了\N{\rENG}It's Frankie's guys. They're back!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.39,1:10:07.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,除了他们，每几个小时就有一群不同的人进来打我\N{\rENG}Them too! Every couple of hours a different bunch comes slapping me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.23,1:10:10.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,别像个孬种一样地抱怨了，拿着你的枪\N{\rENG}Stop whining like a cunt and get your piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.07,1:10:18.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不能这样做\N{\rENG}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.07,1:10:22.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,别再让我看到你\N{\rENG}Don't let me see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.84,1:10:26.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,绝不要让我再见到你\N{\rENG}Don't ever let me see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.88,1:10:37.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,晚上好，伙计，很高兴见到你啊\N{\rENG}Good evening, fellas. Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.76,1:10:41.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,废话少说，他在哪里？\N{\rENG}Never mind the bullshit. Where the fuck is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.85,1:10:42.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,就在这儿，萨尔\N{\rENG}Over here, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.40,1:11:00.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你失败了\N{\rENG}You lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.38,1:12:26.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,她是谁？\N{\rENG}Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.21,1:12:29.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,她带我找到了他的女朋友\N{\rENG}She brought me to the girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.88,1:12:33.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,她得确认一下尸体，所以她有点害怕\N{\rENG}She just had to identify the body, so she's a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.95,1:12:37.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你今早吃早饭了吗？ - 当然\N{\rENG}- Did you have breakfast this morning?  - Of course
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.46,1:12:40.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,很好，场面不会很好看的\N{\rENG}Good. Because it ain't pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.77,1:12:52.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\rENG}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.97,1:12:55.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,他杀了艾利和另外三个人\N{\rENG}He killed Allie and 3 of the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.74,1:12:58.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,事情很不妙\N{\rENG}This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.81,1:13:00.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们去把理查找出来\N{\rENG}Let's go find Richie.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.08,1:13:06.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,澳·凯利，上楼叫人拍照取证\N{\rENG}O'IKelly, get upstairs and make them photograph that thing right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.58,1:13:16.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是我在鲍勃的书桌里发现的\N{\rENG}This is what I found in Bobby's desk.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.65,1:13:21.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,鲍勃同时跟这个和车里的那个上床\N{\rENG}Bobby was doing this one and the one in the car at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.42,1:13:26.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,从尸体的状态来看，我推断…\N{\rENG}Now, from the extreme rigor mortis in the body, it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.83,1:13:30.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡时间是二十四小时以前，在鲍勃之前\N{\rENG}...time of death, 24 hours ago. Before Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.43,1:13:34.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我受够了这个案子了\N{\rENG}I'm getting too old for this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.77,1:13:36.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你的意思\N{\rENG}I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.13,1:14:05.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿，小声点，我妹妹在睡觉\N{\rENG}Hey, keep it down. My sister's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.70,1:14:09.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,把她叫醒我们就不会打扰到你们了，对吧？\N{\rENG}Wake her up. We ain't disturbing yous, are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.21,1:14:11.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,里卡，过来\N{\rENG}Rica, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.37,1:14:14.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们要开一个小派对\N{\rENG}We're wanting a little party.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.65,1:14:18.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,一个小派对\N{\rENG}I want a little party.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.65,1:14:21.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我的离别派对，对吧，鲍勃？\N{\rENG}It's kind of my going- away party. Right, Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.45,1:14:22.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错，理查\N{\rENG}Right, Rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.01,1:14:25.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,你没什么意见吧？\N{\rENG}You ain't got a problem with that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.89,1:14:27.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有，理查，没问题\N{\rENG}No, Rich. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.22,1:14:39.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,安琪儿？帮我接通吉诺，我是皮克利诺\N{\rENG}Angie? Get me Gino. It's Picolino.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.56,1:14:43.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,给一个叫威利的拉皮条的打电话，叫他把最好的女人带来\N{\rENG}Call up Willy the Pimp. You tell him to send over his best broads.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.76,1:14:46.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样就没人会说你是为了钱才和我混的\N{\rENG}Nobody will say you hung out with me just for the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.47,1:14:55.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,理查，拜托，不要这样\N{\rENG}Richie, please, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.41,1:15:00.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来伺候你，理查\N{\rENG}I'll take care of you, Rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.75,1:15:02.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来伺候你，理查\N{\rENG}I'll take care of you, Rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.85,1:15:05.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿，大伙！\N{\rENG}Hey, boys!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.92,1:15:09.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们今晚有福享了\N{\rENG}We're going to have us a real good time tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.92,1:15:12.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,大日子啊，理查，大日子\N{\rENG}Big time, Richie. Big time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.59,1:15:15.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是我的晚上，我的最后一晚\N{\rENG}It's my night! My last night!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.20,1:15:24.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 谁？ - 吉诺\N{\rENG}- Who is it?  - Gino.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.61,1:15:33.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还好吗，劳拉\N{\rENG}How you doing, Laura?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.88,1:15:36.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,很好，维克走了以后我睡不着觉\N{\rENG}Good. Okay. I couldn't sleep after Vick left.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.95,1:15:39.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我洗了个澡，现在好多了\N{\rENG}So I had a bath. I'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.22,1:15:51.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\N{\rENG}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.22,1:15:53.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在找什么？\N{\rENG}What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.29,1:15:57.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,不，不，吉诺，那是我的钱包\N{\rENG}No. No, Gino, that's my purse.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.96,1:15:59.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,快还给我，吉诺，快停下！\N{\rENG}Give me... Gino, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.87,1:16:07.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\rENG}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.14,1:16:11.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\rENG}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.74,1:16:14.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是不是理查杀了鲍勃以后扔下的东西？\N{\rENG}Is this what Richie threw on Bobby after he shot him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.81,1:16:17.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,思维真快啊\N{\rENG}That was fast thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.75,1:16:20.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,不愧是个警察的妻子\N{\rENG}Just like a good cop's wife would.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.08,1:16:23.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道我是怎么想的吗？\N{\rENG}You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.65,1:16:25.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为你一发现这个东西…\N{\rENG}I think you found one of these somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.02,1:16:28.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,…你就光火得很，不敢正眼看它\N{\rENG}And got so fucking mad you couldn't see straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.66,1:16:33.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以你寄了一张给理查，却做梦也没想到他会杀了鲍勃\N{\rENG}So you sent one to Richie, never dreaming he might actually kill Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.83,1:16:38.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我拿走照片是因为我想保护他\N{\rENG}I only took it because I wanted to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.67,1:16:41.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看，这就是洛葛仙妮\N{\rENG}See, this is Roxanne, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.57,1:16:46.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,才二十四岁，理查先杀了她\N{\rENG}Twenty-four years old. Richie killed her first.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.68,1:16:48.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,你错了，吉诺\N{\rENG}You got it all wrong, Gino.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.18,1:16:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我把它拿走只是不想让人知道\N{\rENG}I only took it so people wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.45,1:16:53.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,鲍勃很肮脏，对吧？\N{\rENG}Bobby was dirty, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.67,1:16:56.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许…\N{\rENG}Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.39,1:16:59.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,…他碰巧也在和理查的女人上床\N{\rENG}...he was just doing Richie's girlfriend at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.91,1:17:01.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不那么认为\N{\rENG}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.18,1:17:05.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为鲍勃一直想学另一个人\N{\rENG}I think that Bobby always wanted to be like somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.32,1:17:10.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,他喜欢理查的生活方式，他的钱，他的女人，你知道他是个肮脏的人\N{\rENG}He liked Richie's lifestyle, his money, his women. You knew he was dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.99,1:17:13.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,鲍勃已经走了，其他人也都走了\N{\rENG}Bobby's gone now. So are lots of other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.73,1:17:15.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想杀他\N{\rENG}I didn't want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.99,1:17:18.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是想拯救我的婚姻\N{\rENG}I just wanted to save my marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.13,1:17:20.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来，劳丽，过来\N{\rENG}Come here, Laurie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.70,1:17:25.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要我的鲍勃回来\N{\rENG}I want my Bobby back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.74,1:17:27.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要他回来\N{\rENG}I want him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.81,1:17:35.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}皮克利诺有急事找你\N{\rENG\i1}You have an emergency phone call from Picolino.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.88,1:17:37.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,安琪儿，帮我转接\N{\rENG}Angie, patch me through right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.30,1:17:43.89,ZHU,,0,0,0,,一个和理查有过来往的妓女就住在我格里高利叔叔的隔壁
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.09,1:17:46.09,ZHU,,0,0,0,,我想理查正在亲热呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.43,1:17:49.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,听着，皮克利诺，我知道那个地方\N{\rENG}Listen to me, Picolino. I know that place.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.03,1:17:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,马上离开那里，立刻！\N{\rENG}Get out of the neighborhood now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.40,1:17:54.40,ZHU,,0,0,0,,我这就走
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.87,1:21:01.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,把手放在桌子上！\N{\rENG}Hands on the table!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.67,1:21:02.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rENG}What the fuck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.69,1:21:21.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我兄弟吉诺来了\N{\rENG}My buddy Gino's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.39,1:21:25.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要去和他玩玩了\N{\rENG}I got to go play.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.34,1:22:18.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,去你的，臭警察！\N{\rENG}Fuck you, cop!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.12,1:22:33.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,他在浴室里\N{\rENG}He's in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.09,1:22:50.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想怎么做，啊？\N{\rENG}What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.29,1:22:53.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想怎么做？逮捕我吗？\N{\rENG}What're you going to do, you going to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.23,1:22:55.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,我没子弹了！\N{\rENG}I'm out of bullets!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.97,1:23:01.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾\N{\rENG}That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.67,1:23:04.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些子弹原本可以帮你省去许多痛苦的\N{\rENG}Those bullets could've saved you a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.74,1:23:06.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢痛苦\N{\rENG}I like pain, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.31,1:24:55.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要杀了你\N{\rENG}I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.12,1:25:05.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是替鲍勃还的\N{\rENG}That's for Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.11,1:25:11.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 吉诺，发生了什么？ - 我中弹了，这里中了一弹\N{\rENG}- What happened?  - I'm hit. Took one right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.09,1:25:14.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,你拿我的枪干什么？\N{\rENG}What're you doing with my gun?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.09,1:25:19.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？天啊！\N{\rENG}What the hell is wrong with you? Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.39,1:25:21.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你做的是对的  - 我做的是对的？\N{\rENG}- You did the right thing.  - I did the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.03,1:25:27.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,很抱歉事情不得不这样收场\N{\rENG}I'm sorry it had to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.63,1:25:30.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,告诉老大你做的事，然后搞个仪式\N{\rENG}Tell the boss what you did. Do the ritual thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.43,1:25:31.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有病吗？\N{\rENG}Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.70,1:25:35.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,把他扔到杰西的箱子里算了\N{\rENG}Geez, put him in a fucking trunk in Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.70,1:25:38.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,听上去很不错，但是…\N{\rENG}That sounds great, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.81,1:25:42.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,…我们能到城里吃顿饭吗？就我和你\N{\rENG}...can we have dinner in the city, me and you alone sometime?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.88,1:25:45.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然，我连寻呼机都不会带的\N{\rENG}Sure, I won't even bring my beeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.81,1:25:48.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,说起吃的，我想要吃…\N{\rENG}Speaking of food, I could go for...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.42,1:25:51.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,带奶酪的辣热狗和薯条\N{\rENG}...a chili hot dog with cheese and french fries.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.35,1:25:56.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,还是别吃了，现在已经上午九点了，吃了你中饭就吃不下了\N{\rENG}Not for nothing. It's 9 a. m. Eat here, you'll have gangrene by noon.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.53,1:26:00.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,吉诺，我要给你买一个浪漫的…\N{\rENG}Gino, I'm going to buy you a nice romantic...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.90,1:26:09.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿，你！\N{\rENG}Yo, fucknuts!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.24,1:26:12.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在跟我说话吗？\N{\rENG}You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.81,1:26:16.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,那天是不是你从车上扔下一条狗？\N{\rENG}Are you the guy who threw a puppy out this car window the other day?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.94,1:26:20.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 关你什么事？ - 我喜欢动物\N{\rENG}- What's your business, anyway?  - I'm an animal lover.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.38,1:26:21.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,喜欢动物？\N{\rENG}Animal lover?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.48,1:26:25.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,你管好你自己的事吧，不然我就扁你一顿…\N{\rENG}You don't mind your fucking business, I'll stuff you in a bag...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.15,1:26:28.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你也从车窗里扔出去！\N{\rENG}...and throw you out a fucking window.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.29,1:26:30.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你很有种嘛  - 我就叫你看看我的厉害\N{\rENG}- You're a tough guy?  - I'll show you how tough I am.
